commit_message:
230418: Fix small bug in table reading functions that produced a warning.
imp_commandline.pl and sequence_imp.pl affected.

171117: Incorporate pipefail into a number of commands as a safety measure.
Fix issue 4 (drop.self for ignoreSelf in findOverlaps).
280317: Updated CHANGELOG with latest version change.

060317: Corresponds with release version 17-055
Update changelog and authors list to account for most recent additions.

Merge branch 'master' of https://github.com/davis-m/SequenceImp this incorporates
changes from tleonardi.
220217: Modified change log to include recent changes.

Merge pull request #2 from tleonardi/master

Fixes issue #1 "when aligning a file in which the vast majority of reads map to a single Ensembl category and all other categories have less then 1% of the reads each, Seqimp "align" gives error"

220217: Corresponds to version 17-053.
Edited trimming configuration to anchor -3p-prefix.
Edit the read names in paired end clean-up to ensure paired reads have matching IDs.
Add add_read_index.pl to add a pair index to paired end read IDs.
Begin implementing more streamlined testing to ease continued development (t/). Add paired end testing.

041016: Updated pipeline to work with the latest samtools versions. Include
version check as some alterations to samtools sort are not compatible with
earlier samtools versions.
15-127: Fixed Bowtie annotation plots to cope when either repeat annotation or gene annotation have no classes that surpass the threshold to plot individually
v15-075: Solve default collapse_method passing, remove underscores from R options, update README
